hackathon-description-text: This weekend, HackUCI changes Orange County forever. This is 36 hours of intense learning and building concluding in an expo of awesome tech projects. Join us as we close the spring collegiate hackathon season in style!
hackathon-eligibility: Primarily for students in college. High schools also accepted.
hackathon-requirements: Make something you think is awesome!
hackathon-rules: Your project must be created at HackUCI

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Immersion Summit + DK2 preorder by OCVR

hackathon-prizes.prize-title: Best Hack using the Rdio API
Best Hack using the SendGrid API
Best Hack using the Twilio API

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Hack dojo 8 weeks summer program + $500 scholarship to Full-stack Jr Web Developer 10 week program.
$100 towards any evening GA workshops or events on campus.

hackathon-location-google-maps: https://maps.google.com/?q=1691 Kettering Street, Irvine, CA 92614, USA
